{"word":"πλινθεύω","slug":"πλινθεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πλινθεύω</b></el> <el>(πλινθεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πλίνθος'><el>πλίνθος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to make into bricks</i>, <el>τὴν γῆν</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to make bricks</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>;—so in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <a href='S:Thucydides'>thuc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to build of brick</i>, <el>τείχη</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to make in the form of a plinth</i> or <i>brick</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}